{"tid":797052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？ 廢老巴士上跌死，司機被判入獄4星期，上訴遭駁回","createTime":"2018-08-28T08:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T15:17:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4279b53b933f19a6f439eee8e94e06be04bee7c","tid":797052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"一名九巴司機去年6月28日晚在青衣駕駛巴士抵總站上客時，未有待乘客坐定便開車，導致一名年逾70歲的男乘客跌倒，頭部受傷，數日後傷重不治。司機事後向警方訛稱出事時巴士尚未開動，但警方事後聯絡到車上乘客揭發他說謊。司機經審訊後被判企圖誤導警務人員罪成及即時監禁4星期，他早前提出上訴，高等法院今(28日)頒下判決書，駁回他就定罪提出的上訴，但改判緩刑18個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180828/bkn-20180828152647951-0828_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180828%2Fbkn-20180828152647951-0828_00822_001.html&d=VNmlqQ1PE7hT5e2WvJGzcTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=af2f45b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180828/bkn-20180828152647951-0828_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c2995eaef80d65904f5c2c888049b33b755af6a","tid":797052,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"返工-----&gt;Virtual Jail------&gt;Real Jail"},{"pid":"3390d50940e7aa5187817dcb9742e8f12d82d9a4","tid":797052,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"★[又贏]社署周四向領綜援學生發放$2000津貼  毋須另行申請<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/796853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/796853</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a0fd2697ac3dfd148208c370cd998f61317589a","tid":797052,"uid":29270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"司機事後向警方訛稱出事時巴士尚未開動，但警方事後聯絡到車上乘客揭發他說謊。司機經審訊後被判企圖誤導警務人員罪成及即時監禁4星期。<br />\n<br />\n扺死喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef98dc6cd74d6